race.description: Corowa Chaff Mill Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: Very weak field with the exception of NEESON (6) who charged home late to get up for second when resuming over 1100m at Nowra last start. Beautifully placed over an extra furlong and this looks his race to lose. COMMANDING SHADOW (1) is a 14-start maiden who found 1000m a bit slick at Balranald last time. Led and just failed to hang on over 1200m at Wagga Riverside three back - poses a threat if he finds that form. INSTIGATE (7) has showed pace but failed to finish off in her three runs to date, all in shorter races. Less pressure today so might offer a bit more in the final stages. LAUNCH MODE (3) resumes. Has been in the money seven times so isn't hopeless. Will be better for this run but can sneak into the frame. Hard to see the others making any waves.
